@@TJvThreadTimer.Destroy
Summary
  Destroys an instance of TJvThreadTimer
Description
  Do not call Destroy directly in an application. Instead, call Free. Free verifies that the
  TJvThreadTimer object is not nil and only then calls Destroy.
See Also
  TJvThreadTimer.Create

