@@TJvThreadTimer.Create
Summary
  Creates and initializes a new TJvThreadTimer object.
Description
  Use \Create to create and initialize a new TJvThreadTimer object.
  
  \Create calls the inherited \Create method, creates a thread and then sets the initial values for
  the timer as follows:
  
  * Interval is set to 100.
  * Enabled is set to false.
  * Priority is set to tpNormal
  * KeepAlive is set to false.
Parameters
  AOwner - A component, typically the form, that is responsible for freeing the timer.
See Also
  TJvThreadTimer.Interval

